---
import SectionContainer from "../../ui/SectionContainer.astro";
import CTAGroup from "../../ui/CTAGroup.astro";
---

<section class="bg-[#04101f] py-24 md:py-32 spotlight">
  <SectionContainer>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
      <!-- Section label -->
      <p class="text-[#3BA6FF] tracking-[0.25em] text-xs text-center mb-4">
        CONSULTATION
      </p>

      <!-- Heading -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-white text-3xl md:text-5xl font-semibold leading-tight tracking-tight">
          Book Your Free Suspension Eligibility Review
        </h2>

        <p class="mt-5 text-white/72 text-base md:text-lg leading-8">
          In a 30-minute consultation, we review the suspension, assess the likely
          policy trigger, and determine whether recovery is realistically possible.
          If the account is eligible, you leave with clear next steps.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Main content -->
      <div class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr] items-stretch">
        <!-- Left: what happens -->
        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-[#081826] p-6 md:p-8 shadow-[0_0_0_1px_rgba(255,255,255,0.02)]">
          <h3 class="text-white text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">
            What happens on the call
          </h3>

          <div class="space-y-5">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#3BA6FF]/12 border border-[#3BA6FF]/25 text-[#3BA6FF] font-semibold">
                1
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-white font-medium text-base md:text-lg">
                  Account Review
                </h4>
                <p class="mt-1 text-white/68 leading-7 text-sm md:text-base">
                  We inspect the suspension context, account history, and visible
                  business signals to understand what may have triggered the issue.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#3BA6FF]/12 border border-[#3BA6FF]/25 text-[#3BA6FF] font-semibold">
                2
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-white font-medium text-base md:text-lg">
                  Recovery Assessment
                </h4>
                <p class="mt-1 text-white/68 leading-7 text-sm md:text-base">
                  We assess likely recoverability and identify whether the case
                  appears viable before any structured appeal work begins.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#3BA6FF]/12 border border-[#3BA6FF]/25 text-[#3BA6FF] font-semibold">
                3
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-white font-medium text-base md:text-lg">
                  Clear Next Steps
                </h4>
                <p class="mt-1 text-white/68 leading-7 text-sm md:text-base">
                  You get a direct outline of what should happen next, whether that
                  means proceeding with recovery work or being told honestly that
                  the case is unlikely to succeed.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: reassurance / decision card -->
        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(59,166,255,0.10),rgba(8,24,38,1))] p-6 md:p-8">
          <h3 class="text-white text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold mb-5">
            What this review is designed to do
          </h3>

          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm md:text-base leading-7 text-white/72">
            <p>
              This is not a generic sales call. It is a live suspension eligibility
              review focused on clarity, risk, and next-step direction.
            </p>

            <p>
              We look at whether the suspension is potentially recoverable, what
              documentation or structural fixes may be required, and whether it
              makes sense to proceed.
            </p>

            <p>
              If the account does not appear viable, that will be stated directly.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="my-7 h-px w-full bg-white/10"></div>

          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm md:text-base text-white/80">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="mt-2 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[#3BA6FF]"></span>
              <span>30-minute live review</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="mt-2 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[#3BA6FF]"></span>
              <span>Policy trigger assessment</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="mt-2 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[#3BA6FF]"></span>
              <span>Recoverability determination</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="mt-2 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[#3BA6FF]"></span>
              <span>Structured next-step outline</span>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <p class="mt-7 text-xs md:text-sm text-white/50 leading-6">
            Due to manual case preparation, we review a limited number of new
            suspension cases each week.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="mt-12 flex justify-center">
        <CTAGroup
          href="https://calendly.com/gianluca-adrestore/30min-consultation"
          text="Book Suspension Review"
          assessmentText="Free 30-Minute Live Account Assessment"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </SectionContainer>
</section>